reviewText:
There are only three episodes on this disc which can be fond on the main volumes.
Episodes on this volume are:
1. Bone Diggers (also found on Dinosaur & Other Animal Adventures)
2. Pet Matchers (also found on All you Need is Love and Pasta)
3. Luck Charm (also found on Summertime Adventures)
There are no Garfield short on this volume either.
